Class ParkingSpot

  • java.lang.Object
    • ParkingSpot

  • public class ParkingSpot
extends java.lang.Object
    Following Java class ParkingSpot includes There are two types of parking spots: spots for everyone and spots only for disabled persons. A parking spot have an identifier, which starts with a capital letter, followed by a two-digit number e.g. “D01”, “E27”. A parking spot also know if and what a car is parked in the spot. It able to add a car to the spot and remove a car from the spot.
